# Chromium child-process debug logs at repo root.
# Per v0.3.0 ideas doc ticket 6 (mitigation path c). Electron's
# main-process --log-file flag is not inherited by renderer/GPU/
# utility children on Windows GUI builds; they fall back to
# writing PID-named debug logs to the parent process's cwd.
/[0-9]*
